{"type": "article", "id": 13893, "title": "金色气泡灯具", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-24T08:03:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060002453mk2i1vUtnIEZYdQ.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是英国设计工作室 Tangent Design 最近推出的一款特别的灯具，他们把粘稠的物质填充在陶瓷容器里面，顶部是黑色硅油薄膜，底部是 LED 灯泡，当小水泵把空气送上去，发光的气泡也会随之升上去，实现了金色气泡闪动的效果，结合黑色的背景色，看上去非常神秘和庄严。 Tangent Design 一直以来以特殊的照明设计著名，<a href=\"http://www.tangent.uk.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141537Fh438PerD9zWlsan.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6601467\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141538ZtbCf9NcqYTDwSUa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141540wfbSKl07nxJG6Qgz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261415400jypg3zOmeoMUwli.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141541q5mcDpMTyQtUBuO6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141541G2Fn8Qe5djqEO0A9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}